8月2日晚間，蘇迪羅以[[薩菲爾-辛普森颶風等級|薩菲爾-辛普森颶風等級]]中，二級颱風的強度橫過[[塞班島|塞班島]]<ref>{{cite report |author=Kenneth R. Kleeschulte |work=National Weather Service Office in Tiyan, Guam |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2015-08-02 |accessdate=2015-08-04 |title=Typhoon Soudelor (13W) Intermediate Advisory Number 13A |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtpq31.pgum.tcp.pq1.txt |archivedate=2015-08-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6aUKMr7xG?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ31-PGUM_201508021245.htm |deadurl=yes }}{{en}}</ref>，並對該島造成廣泛的破壞<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Radio New Zealand|date=2015-08-03|accessdate=2015-08-04|title=Severe typhoon damage on CNMI's Saipan|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/280382/severe-typhoon-damage-on-cnmi%27s-saipan|archive-date=2018-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912092230/https://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/280382/severe-typhoon-damage-on-cnmi's-saipan|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。而[[国家气象局_(美国)|美國國家氣象局]]在[[塞班國際機場|塞班國際機場]]的[[风速计|风速计]]則錄得{{convert|91|mph|km/h|abbr=on|disp=flip}}的最高陣風風速。強風將島上的樹木和電力線吹倒，導致島上大部分地方停電<ref>{{cite web|author=Clynt Ridgell|publisher=Pacific News Center|date=2015-08-03|accessdate=2015-08-04|title=Typhoon Soudelor Slams Saipan|url=http://www.pacificnewscenter.com/local/item/4930-typhoon-soudelor-slams-saipan|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805021239/http://www.pacificnewscenter.com/local/item/4930-typhoon-soudelor-slams-saipan|archive-date=2015-08-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，亦造成當地多處房屋倒塌。在該島的電力基礎設施嚴重受損，150個電源桿和114個[[變壓器|變壓器]]受損或損壞<ref>{{cite news|agency=Associated Press|publisher=''Washington Times''|date=2015-08-05|accessdate=2015-08-05|title=Saipan: Restoring essential services could take a month|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2015/aug/5/saipan-restoring-essential-services-could-take-a-m/|location=[[阿加尼亚|阿加尼亚]]|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319215326/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2015/aug/5/saipan-restoring-essential-services-could-take-a-m/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但當地電力公司僅備有77根電線桿供替換。當地觀測站實測中心最低氣壓為{{convert|938.8|hPa|inHg}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://i.imgur.com/vffzQU7.gif|title=北馬里亞納群島塞班島近中心最低氣壓測量報告|date=3-8-2015|access-date=2015-08-03|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319222901/https://i.imgur.com/vffzQU7.gif|dead-url=no}}</ref>初步估計塞班島因蘇迪勒颱風損失超過2000萬美元。<ref name=RNZI>{{cite web|title=CNMI count costs for Soudelor damage|url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/280553/cnmi-count-costs-for-soudelor-damage|website=Radio New Zealand International|publisher=Radio New Zealand International|accessdate=2015-08-05}}</ref>此外，[[美國紅十字會|美國紅十字會]]的約翰·赫希指，蘇迪羅是自[[1986年太平洋颱風季|1986年]]的颱風甘茵，於近三十年襲擊該島以來最具破壞性的熱帶氣旋<ref>{{cite web|title=Typhoon Soudelor becomes world's most powerful storm this year after it trashes Northern Marianas|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-08-04/typhoon-soudelor-state-of-emergency-declared/6672798|website=ABC News|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2015-08-05|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319222916/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-08-04/typhoon-soudelor-state-of-emergency-declared/6672798|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。
